  69,34,"yuqal likhazanat jhnm: khudhuu hdha almujrim alathym, fa'ajmieuu yadayh 'iilaa eunuqih balaghlal, thuma adkhlwh aljahim lyqasy hrha, thuma fi silsilat min hadid tuluha sabeun dhraeana fadkhlwh fyha; 'iinah kan la ysddiq bi'ana allah hu al'ilh alhaqu wahdah la sharik lh, wala yaemal bhdyh, wala yhth alnaas fi aldunya ealaa 'iiteam 'ahl alhajat min almsakyn wghyrhm"
  69,35,"flys lhdha alkafir yawm alqiamat qarib yadfae eanh aledhab, walays lah taeam 'iilaa min sadid 'ahl alnar, laa yakuluh 'iilaa almdhnbwn almsrrun ealaa alkufr ballh"
  69,36,"flys lhdha alkafir yawm alqiamat qarib yadfae eanh aledhab, walays lah taeam 'iilaa min sadid 'ahl alnar, laa yakuluh 'iilaa almdhnbwn almsrrun ealaa alkufr ballh"
  69,37,"flys lhdha alkafir yawm alqiamat qarib yadfae eanh aledhab, walays lah taeam 'iilaa min sadid 'ahl alnar, laa yakuluh 'iilaa almdhnbwn almsrrun ealaa alkufr ballh"
  69,38,"fla 'uqsim bima tubsirun min almryyat, wama la tubsirun mimaa ghab enkm, 'iina alquran lakalam allh, ytlwh rasul eazim alsharaf walfdl, walays biqawl shaeir kama tzemwn, qalilana maa twmnwn, walays bsje ksje alkhan, qalilana maa yakun minkum tdhkkur wtammul llfrq bynhma, wlknh kalam rabu alealamin aldhy 'anzalah ealaa rasulih muhamad salaa allah ealayh wslm"
  69,39,"fla 'uqsim bima tubsirun min almryyat, wama la tubsirun mimaa ghab enkm, 'iina alquran lakalam allh, ytlwh rasul eazim alsharaf walfdl, walays biqawl shaeir kama tzemwn, qalilana maa twmnwn, walays bsje ksje alkhan, qalilana maa yakun minkum tdhkkur wtammul llfrq bynhma, wlknh kalam rabu alealamin aldhy 'anzalah ealaa rasulih muhamad salaa allah ealayh wslm"
  69,40,"fala 'uqsim bima tubsirun min almryyat, wama la tubsirun mimaa ghab enkm, 'iina alquran lakalam allh, ytlwh rasul eazim alsharaf walfdl, walays biqawl shaeir kama tzemwn, qalilana maa twmnwn, walays bsje ksje alkhan, qalilana maa yakun minkum tdhkkur wtammul llfrq bynhma, wlknh kalam rabu alealamin aldhy 'anzalah ealaa rasulih muhamad salaa allah ealayh wslm"
  69,41,"fla 'uqsim bima tubsirun min almryyat, wama la tubsirun mimaa ghab enkm, 'iina alquran lakalam allh, ytlwh rasul eazim alsharaf walfdl, walays biqawl shaeir kama tzemwn, qalilana maa twmnwn, walays bsje ksje alkhan, qalilana maa yakun minkum tdhkkur wtammul llfrq bynhma, wlknh kalam rabu alealamin aldhy 'anzalah ealaa rasulih muhamad salaa allah ealayh wslm"
  69,42,"fla 'uqsim bima tubsirun min almryyat, wama la tubsirun mimaa ghab enkm, 'iina alquran lakalam allh, ytlwh rasul eazim alsharaf walfdl, walays biqawl shaeir kama tzemwn, qalilana maa twmnwn, walays bsje ksje alkhan, qalilana maa yakun minkum tdhkkur wtammul llfrq bynhma, wlknh kalam rabu alealamin aldhy 'anzalah ealaa rasulih muhamad salaa allah ealayh wslm"
  69,43,"fla 'uqsim bima tubsirun min almryyat, wama la tubsirun mimaa ghab enkm, 'iina alquran lakalam allh, ytlwh rasul eazim alsharaf walfdl, walays biqawl shaeir kama tzemwn, qalilana maa twmnwn, walays bsje ksje alkhan, qalilana maa yakun minkum tdhkkur wtammul llfrq bynhma, wlknh kalam rabu alealamin aldhy 'anzalah ealaa rasulih muhamad salaa allah ealayh wslm"
  69,44,"wlw addaea muhamad ealayna shyyana lm nqlh, lantqmna wa'akhadhna minh balymyn, thuma laqataena minh nyat qlbh, fala yuqadar ahd minkum 'ana yhjz eanh eqabna. 'iina hdha alquran lezt lilmutaqin aladhin ymtthlwn 'awamir allah wyjtnbwn nwahyh"
  69,45,"walaw addaea muhamad ealayna shyyana lm nqlh, lantqmna wa'akhadhna minh balymyn, thuma laqataena minh nyat qlbh, fala yuqadar ahd minkum 'ana yhjz eanh eqabna. 'iina hdha alquran lezt lilmutaqin aladhin ymtthlwn 'awamir allah wyjtnbwn nwahyh"
  69,46,"wlw addaea muhamad ealayna shyyana lm nqlh, lantqmna wa'akhadhna minh balymyn, thuma laqataena minh nyat qlbh, fala yuqadar ahd minkum 'ana yhjz eanh eqabna. 'iina hdha alquran lezt lilmutaqin aladhin ymtthlwn 'awamir allah wyjtnbwn nwahyh"
  69,47,"wlw addaea muhamad ealayna shyyana lm nqlh, lantqmna wa'akhadhna minh balymyn, thuma laqataena minh nyat qlbh, fala yuqadar ahd minkum 'ana yhjz eanh eqabna. 'iina hdha alquran lezt lilmutaqin aladhin ymtthlwn 'awamir allah wyjtnbwn nwahyh"
  69,48,"wlw addaea muhamad ealayna shyyana lm nqlh, lantqmna wa'akhadhna minh balymyn, thuma laqataena minh nyat qlbh, fala yuqadar ahd minkum 'ana yhjz eanh eqabna. 'iina hdha alquran lezt lilmutaqin aladhin ymtthlwn 'awamir allah wyjtnbwn nwahyh"
  69,49,"'ina lanelm ann minkm man ykdhdhib bhdha alquran mae wuduh ayath, wa'iin altkdhyb bih lndamt ezymt ealaa alkafirin bih hin yarawn edhabhm wyrwn naeim almuminin bh, wa'iinah lahaqu thabt wyqyn la shaka fyh. fnzzih allah subhanah eamaa la ylyq bjlalh, wadhkrh basmh alezym"
  69,50,"'ina lanelm ann minkm man ykdhdhib bhdha alquran mae wuduh ayath, wa'iin altkdhyb bih lndamt ezymt ealaa alkafirin bih hin yarawn edhabhm wyrwn naeim almuminin bh, wa'iinah lahaqu thabt wyqyn la shaka fyh. fnzzih allah subhanah eamaa la ylyq bjlalh, wadhkrh basmh alezym"
